makkala bhagya ( kannada : ಮಕ bhagya ಭಾಗ ಯ ) is a 1976 indian kannada film , directed by k. s. l. swamy and produced by k. s. l. swamy and produced by k. s. l. swamy . the film stars vishnuvardhan , bharathi , k. s. ashwath and balakrishna in lead roles . the film had musical score by vijaya bhaskar .